    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'll try the breathing stuff. i'm just really worried about the cost of going back to the clinic and the hassle. do you think if i just increase my albuterol inhaler dose by a few extra puffs every time i feel that tightness in my chest it would be okay? i just want to manage it myself so i don't have to keep making appointments.",
